Baervan Wildwanderer is the gnomish Power of the outdoors, forest-dwelling gnomes and their communities, as well as thievery. He is a good-natured trickster, as are the many of the Lords+of+the+Golden+Hills and the friend of many other powers of the forest. He is attended by his long time companion, a giant raccoon named Chiktikka Fastpaws. His Realm is called Whisperleaf and can be found in the Golden Hills of Bytopia. 
Source: Monster Mythology, Demihuman Deities